@theme @theme_charteredcollege @theme_charteredcollege_course
Feature: A teacher should not see the link to message him/herself

  Background:
    Given the following "courses" exist:
      | fullname | shortname | category | format | enablecompletion |
      | Course 1 | C1        | 0        | topics | 1                |
    And the following "users" exist:
      | username | firstname | lastname | email |
      | teacher1 | Teacher | 1 | teacher1@example.com |
      | teacher2 | Teacher | 2 | teacher2@example.com |
      | student1 | Student | 1 | student1@example.com |
    And the following "course enrolments" exist:
      | user | course | role |
      | teacher1 | C1 | editingteacher |
      | teacher2 | C1 | editingteacher |
      | student1 | C1 | student |
    And the following config values are set as admin:
      | theme_charteredcollege_coursefootertoggle | 1 |

  @javascript
  Scenario: As a teacher i should not see a link to message myself
    Given I log in as "teacher1"
    And I am on the course main page for "C1"
    And I should see "Course Contacts"
    And I should see "Teacher 1" in the "#charteredcollege-course-footer .charteredcollege-media-object" "css_element"
    And I should see "Teacher 2" in the "#charteredcollege-course-footer .charteredcollege-media-object:nth-child(3)" "css_element"
    And I should not see "message" in the "#charteredcollege-course-footer .charteredcollege-media-object" "css_element"
    And I should see "message" in the "#charteredcollege-course-footer .charteredcollege-media-object:nth-child(3)" "css_element"
    Then I log out
    And I log in as "teacher2"
    And I am on the course main page for "C1"
    And I should see "Course Contacts"
    And I should see "Teacher 1" in the "#charteredcollege-course-footer .charteredcollege-media-object" "css_element"
    And I should see "Teacher 2" in the "#charteredcollege-course-footer .charteredcollege-media-object:nth-child(3)" "css_element"
    And I should see "message" in the "#charteredcollege-course-footer .charteredcollege-media-object" "css_element"
    And I should not see "message" in the "#charteredcollege-course-footer .charteredcollege-media-object:nth-child(3)" "css_element"

  @javascript
  Scenario: As a student i should see a link to message any teacher
    Given I log in as "student1"
    And I am on the course main page for "C1"
    And I should see "Course Contacts"
    And I should see "Teacher 1" in the "#charteredcollege-course-footer .charteredcollege-media-object" "css_element"
    And I should see "Teacher 2" in the "#charteredcollege-course-footer .charteredcollege-media-object:nth-child(3)" "css_element"
    And I should see "message" in the "#charteredcollege-course-footer .charteredcollege-media-object" "css_element"
    And I should see "message" in the "#charteredcollege-course-footer .charteredcollege-media-object:nth-child(3)" "css_element"
